<item>
            <title>[LU-291] echo client to use obd_brw_async</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-291</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now the echo_client is using obd_brw(), preventing it from getting multiple RPCs in flight&lt;br/&gt;
for a single transfer. This hurts performance testing requests &amp;gt; 1 MB in size.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10763">LU-291</key>
            <summary>echo client to use obd_brw_async</summary>
